  <section id="snippets">
    <title>Snippets</title>
    <body>
      <p>
        You can find various examples of Nemerle code in <a ref="http://nemerle.org/svn/nemerle/trunk/snippets/">snippets</a>
        directory in Nemerle source tree. Examples include:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><a ref="http://nemerle.org/svn/nemerle/trunk/snippets/boyer-moore.n">boyer-moore.n</a> -- Boyer-Moore algorithm</li>
        <li><a ref="http://nemerle.org/svn/nemerle/trunk/snippets/knuth-morris-pratt.n">knuth-morris-pratt.n</a> -- Knuth-Morris-Pratt algorithm</li>
        <li><a ref="http://nemerle.org/svn/nemerle/trunk/snippets/lcs.n">lcs.n</a> -- longest common substring</li>
        <li><a ref="http://nemerle.org/svn/nemerle/trunk/snippets/nondec-subseq.n">nondec-subseq.n</a> -- longest non-decreasing subsequence</li>
        <li><a ref="http://nemerle.org/svn/nemerle/trunk/snippets/rachunki.n">rachunki.n</a> -- a billing generator for a conference</li>
        <li><a ref="http://nemerle.org/svn/nemerle/trunk/snippets/shift-or.n">shift-or.n</a> -- shift-or text searching algorithm</li>
        <li><a ref="http://nemerle.org/svn/nemerle/trunk/snippets/sql.n">sql.n</a> -- example of data base connectivity</li>
        <li><a ref="http://nemerle.org/svn/nemerle/trunk/snippets/suffix.n">suffix.n</a> -- suffix trees</li>
        <li><a ref="http://nemerle.org/svn/nemerle/trunk/snippets/myPoll.n">myPoll.n</a> 
        -- example of CGI application connecting to PostgreSQL database</li>
        <li><a ref="http://nemerle.org/svn/nemerle/trunk/snippets/power-race.n">power-race.n</a> --
        a ncurses-based ``game''. <a ref="images/power-race.png">Screenshot.</a></li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        These are also bundled with the source distribution.
      </p>
      <p>
        There are also several more advanced examples there:
      </p>
    </body>
    <subsection id="shootout">
      <title>The Great Language Shootout Examples</title>
      <body>
        <p>
