          ref="http://www.bagley.org/~doug/shootout/">The Great Language
          Shootout</a>. Looking for volunteers to port more.
        </p>
      </body>
    </subsection>
    <subsection id="ntrace">
      <title>ntrace</title>
      <body>
        <p>
          This simple program will trace memory leaks in programs written
          in C. By Jacek Åšliwerski.
        </p>
      </body>
    </subsection>
    <subsection id="sioux">
      <title>Sioux HTTP server</title>
      <body>
        <p>
          A simplistic HTTP server. The main idea behind it is to serve
          web applications written in Nemerle. It already served as a
          subscription server for the XVIII-th FIT (a local conference).
        </p>
      </body>
    </subsection>
